\b0 \cf0 GZDoom is a source port of classic Doom (Ultimate Doom, Doom II, Final Doom), Heretic, Hexen, Strife and other games on Doom engine made by Graf Zahl. It is based on ZDoom by Randy Heit but has OpenGL renderer and many extended features.\
\
Starting from version 0.1.1 the binary distribution contains two application bundles:\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\qj
\ls1\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\'95	}GZDoom_SDL, which is an original SDL-based port the same as old versions.\
{\listtext	\'95	}GZDoom_Cocoa, which is an experimental native Cocoa version. It has a few improvements over SDL version like user-friendly fullscreen mode, support for system shortcuts and some limitations removed. However there are missing features (the most noticeable one is lack of joystick/gamepad support) and may have additional issues.\
\pard\pardeftab720\qj
\cf0 If you play with keyboard/mouse the Cocoa version is preferred. There is no plans to improve SDL version except regular integrations from (G)ZDoom SVN repository.\
\
